token_info.name: The Flag
token_info.description: "The Flag" is a celebration of diversity. Every person has the right to be loved, respected and nurtured. This piece was created exclusively for the #OBJKT4OBJKT campaign of 23-25 April 2021. Please follow @diversenftart on Twitter! Press your mouse and drag, or press the key “c” to change flags. Exclusive on hicetnunc.xyz
